Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.15,0:20:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.86,0:21:04.95,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,450)\pos(642,601)}尼特鲁多帝国 赌场
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.03,0:21:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂喂 那个人是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.19,0:21:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.89,0:21:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而且那个人今天是第一次玩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.99,0:21:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今晚的游戏也很棒啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.29,0:21:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}则利夫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.93,0:21:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.55,0:21:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.03,0:21:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没想到你真的在这种地方玩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.49,0:21:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}给我看清自己的立场
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.27,0:21:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你可是正规军的将军
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.91,0:21:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.87,0:21:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}差不多到出门的时间了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.19,0:21:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}他就是天才则利夫将军啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.89,0:21:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}四个将军一起去 还真是豪华啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.89,0:21:35.86,Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(642,547)}尼特鲁多六将军 无限战士
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.89,0:21:35.86,Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(802,639)}卡维
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.07,0:21:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊 走吧走吧 塞利古
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.65,0:21:40.57,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,450)\pos(636,545)}尼特鲁多六将军 miss零
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.65,0:21:40.57,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,450)\pos(794.667,643)}法尔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.33,0:21:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}最好别小看对手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.53,0:21:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}自傲会自灭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.94,0:21:45.91,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,450)\pos(638.667,545.667)}尼特鲁多六将军 王弟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.94,0:21:45.91,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,450)\pos(803.333,641.667)}格林基
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.55,0:21:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要忘记王兄马科斯的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.47,0:21:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}尼特鲁多的目的只有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.03,0:21:51.00,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,450)\pos(644,547)}尼特鲁多六将军 解决一切谜题之人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.03,0:21:51.00,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,450)\pos(774,643)}则利夫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.25,0:21:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那么 赶快去解决吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.91,0:21:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}英雄阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.29,0:22:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你一个人在这里干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.23,0:22:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}打手枪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.85,0:22:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}特基洛夫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.23,0:22:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}和平时一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.77,0:22:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我还以为你会更加失落
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.49,0:22:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}爸爸的事也不是那么在意
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.83,0:22:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为我已经做好觉悟了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.77,0:22:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}反而可能还有些高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.03,0:22:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我去战斗 然后胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.75,0:22:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}竟然有人会那么开心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.29,0:22:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但我还是不太明白
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.39,0:22:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}同时发生太多事了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.85,0:22:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.39,0:22:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但那就是你选择的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.11,0:22:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.99,0:22:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只拥有力量的人没有人会去称赞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.19,0:22:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就算是软弱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.89,0:22:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}选择了艰辛之路的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.41,0:22:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人们也会去尊敬
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.05,0:22:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}比谁都强大
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.55,0:22:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}比谁都快
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.47,0:22:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}比谁都帅气
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.81,0:22:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我完全比不上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.87,0:22:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}虽然我真的觉得大哥很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.77,0:23:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但我不会尊敬大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.71,0:23:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.57,0:23:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}即使那样我也会一直跑下去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.09,0:23:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}朝向着世界的中心
